    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        This <b>Portfolio</b> contains all the things that I do in my work. I created this portfolio to help me find job more easier. I'm not good at coding but I'm striving for more knowledge in this field. 
        My college major is <b>Network System Technologies</b>, where we focus on creating a secure and effective network system.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://www.facebook.com/franklinmanalastasogot" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-2">My last projects {"</>"}</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
